
use double forward slashes to comment single line

	//Write here program
	
Group comment

	/*
		  Enter forward slash and start and press enter
		  it should end with start and forward slash
	 */
	 
Shortcut to comment existing lines

	=> first select group of lines
	=> then press Control+Shift and Forward slash [control+shift+/]

Shortcut to release commented lines
	=> first select already commented lines
	=> then press Control+Shift and backward slash [control+shift+\]
